'''2020年环意自行车赛'''是第103届[[环意自行车赛|环意自行车赛]]。此次比赛原定于2020年5月9日至31日进行，然而受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，该比赛延期至2020年10月3日开赛，10月25日完赛<ref name =Farrand>{{cite news| url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-reveal-new-mens-and-womens-post-covid-19-race-calendar/| title=UCI reveal new men's and women's post-COVID-19 race calendar| last=Farrand| first=Stephen| work=Cycling News| date=2020-05-05| accessdate=2020-05-05| archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201029085043/https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-reveal-new-mens-and-womens-post-covid-19-race-calendar/| archivedate=2020-10-29}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。此次比赛原定途经匈牙利和法国，然而由于2019冠状病毒病疫情，两国都不允许该届环意自行车赛途经各自领土，最终比赛全程都在意大利境内进行，起点位于[[蒙雷阿莱|蒙雷阿莱]]，终点位于[[米蘭|米蘭]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sporza.be/nl/2020/03/13/officieel-giro-wordt-uitgesteld-na-maatregelen-van-hongaarse-regering~1584099434886/|title=Officieel: Giro wordt uitgesteld na maatregelen van Hongaarse regering|work=Sporza|date=2020-03-13|accessdate=2020-03-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319153038/https://sporza.be/nl/2020/03/13/officieel-giro-wordt-uitgesteld-na-maatregelen-van-hongaarse-regering~1584099434886/|archivedate=2020-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Giro d'Italia: French COVID-19 rules mean Agnello and Izoard cut from stage 20|url=https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/giro-ditalia-french-covid-19-rules-mean-agnello-and-izoard-cut-from-stage-20/|work=Cycling News|accessdate=2020-10-22|date=2020-10-21|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201029085245/https://www.cyclingnews.com/news/giro-ditalia-french-covid-19-rules-mean-agnello-and-izoard-cut-from-stage-20/|archivedate=2020-10-29}}{{cbignore}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.velonews.com/2020-giro-ditalia/2020-giro-ditalia-route-map/|title=2020 Giro d'Italia Route Map|work=VeloNews|accessdate=2020-10-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112212959/https://www.velonews.com/2020-giro-ditalia/2020-giro-ditalia-route-map/|archivedate=2020-11-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中19支为世界职业车队，另外3支为洲际职业车队<ref name="giro-startlist">{{cite web|title=2020 UCI WorldTour races Wild Cards: RCS Sport choices|url=http://www.giroditalia.it/eng/news/2020-uci-worldtour-races-wild-cards-rcs-sport-choices/|publisher=RCS Sport|date=2020-01-16|accessdate=2020-01-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222145503/http://www.giroditalia.it/eng/news/2020-uci-worldtour-races-wild-cards-rcs-sport-choices|archivedate=2020-02-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管2020年10月时，[[2019冠状病毒病意大利疫情|意大利疫情]]出现反弹，途中又有两支队伍因为队内聚集性疫情主动放弃后面的比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://africa.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/30105938/coronavirus-forces-mitchelton-scott-jumbo-visma-teams-withdraw-giro-ditalia|title=Coronavirus forces Mitchelton-Scott and Jumbo-Visma teams to withdraw from Giro d'Italia|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2020-10-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019225007/https://africa.espn.com/olympics/story/_/id/30105938/coronavirus-forces-mitchelton-scott-jumbo-visma-teams-withdraw-giro-ditalia|archivedate=2020-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中断比赛的呼声也随着感染人员数量的增加而日渐高涨<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/cycling/news/21683/12102999/steven-kruijswijk-and-mitchelton-scott-team-out-of-giro-ditalia-after-positive-coronavirus-tests|title=Giro d'Italia on brink of cancellation amid COVID-19 cases as teams withdraw|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2020-10-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20201029085944/https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/cycling/news/21683/12102999/steven-kruijswijk-and-mitchelton-scott-team-out-of-giro-ditalia-after-positive-coronavirus-tests|archivedate=2020-10-29}}</ref>，比赛最终还是按照推迟后的计划完赛。最终来自英力士車隊的[[Tao_Geoghegan_Hart|Tao Geoghegan Hart]]获得此次比赛的总冠军，来自[[太阳网车队|太阳网车队]]的[[Jai_Hindley|Jai Hindley]]和[[Wilco_Kelderman|Wilco Kelderman]]分别获得二三名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/cycling/54679027 |title=Giro d'Italia: Tao Geoghegan Hart wins first Grand Tour |work=BBC Sport |date=2020-10-25 |accessdate=2020-10-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025154204/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/cycling/54679027 |archivedate=2020-10-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

